  ('optometrist-moex-01769', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-109-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '若一個-6.00DS聚碳酸酯鏡片（n=1.586），鏡框彎弧角為20度，鏡片傾斜在臨床上所造成的影響，下列 敘述何者錯誤？', '["鏡框彎弧角為鏡架前框相對於臉部的水平額切面所成的夾角", "鏡框彎弧角並不會影響到鏡片的垂直子午面屈光度", "在軸90度所誘發的柱面屈光度為-0.80DC", "鏡片的等效屈光力為-6.22DS/-0.80DC×090"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "fbe256539a1b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3a63d6395b69", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109060", "c": "401", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試（第一階段考試）、驗船師、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政...", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-01770', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-109-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '位於透鏡左方1公尺的點光源，經+3.00DS/+3.00DC×180的圓柱透鏡（spherocylindricallens）聚焦後，它 的最小模糊圈（circleofleastconfusion）位於鏡片右方多遠之處？', '["22.22公分", "25.00公分", "28.57公分", "33.33公分"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ce0dc77563b8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a1c83f3335a4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
